Set Permissions for Google Cloud Storage Bucket

Set up permissions on your Google Cloud Storage bucket.

In Google Cloud Storage Platform click Cloud Storage.
Under Cloud Storage, click Browser.
Click your bucket name, and click the Permissions tab.
Configure the permissions for the bucket and save.
We support these permission configurations for a bucket.
Public Access - Subject to object ACLs
Access Control - Fine Grained/Uniform
